[b]TVO - The Agenda with Steve Paikin, April 24 2012: A Vision of the Future[/b]

The Agenda looks at our past to imagine our future.

[u]Imagining the Future[/u]

Nobody knows what the future will bring, yet much of our thinking about the present depends on how we imagine the future. The Agenda examines the notion of &quot;future&quot;.

